data.description: 4 Bedroom 3 bathroom 2,240 sq ft home.   Sits on 1.44 acres with oak trees.  Peaceful location with room for pets and animals.   Well maintained and manicured.  Move in ready.  This home has a lot to offer.  With a jetted tub in master bath.  Wood stove in dining room.  Gas fireplace in living room.  Vaulted ceilings.  Large, beautiful kitchen with wood cabinets.  Opens into a spacious living room with a formal dining room attached.  The exterior boasts a deck that encompasses. approximately 60% around the house.   A hot tub that not been connected to electrical.  A raised foundation gives great access with extra storage room below the house.  More storage in large well pump house.  Perimeter fenced with a private gate for entry.
